WEBVTT

1
00:14:17.092 --> 00:14:18.471
No matter.

2
00:14:18.708 --> 00:14:20.790
We are Brothers.

3
01:11:10.375 --> 01:11:13.665
You will never hear
my Song again.

4
01:33:12.022 --> 01:33:15.977
Yes. we must find
Brother of Payakan.

5
01:45:05.625 --> 01:45:07.540
Stand up straight. you idiots.

6
01:45:08.041 --> 01:45:09.915
Do not show fear.

7
01:54:24.041 --> 01:54:25.540
I'm glad to see you.

8
01:54:36.708 --> 01:54:37.874
It is...

9
01:54:38.416 --> 01:54:39.915
Very bad.

10
01:54:43.291 --> 01:54:44.540
I did.

11
01:54:46.125 --> 01:54:49.582
But only one survives.

12
01:54:56.333 --> 01:54:58.457
I am Ta'nok.

13
01:54:59.666 --> 01:55:02.207
Look what they did to me!

14
01:55:03.091 --> 01:55:04.591
Shot me!

15
01:55:04.833 --> 01:55:06.332
Blinded me!

16
01:55:07.750 --> 01:55:11.080
Look what the
Sky People did to me!

17
01:57:46.625 --> 01:57:48.249
I know what they call it.

18
01:57:48.353 --> 01:57:50.499
Then learn to See!

19
01:57:50.678 --> 01:57:53.212
Connect to something
greater than you...

20
01:57:53.215 --> 01:57:56.289
...greater than anything
you've ever known.

21
02:21:35.083 --> 02:21:37.165
My Brother must speak to the council.

22
02:21:37.666 --> 02:21:38.957
Payakan! Go!

23
02:21:39.500 --> 02:21:40.999
You cannot be here.

24
02:30:54.057 --> 02:30:56.934
Payakan. I will lead.

25
02:30:57.291 --> 02:30:59.415
Yes. Matriarch.

26
02:50:39.416 --> 02:50:41.582
Go to the Sky People...

27
02:50:42.541 --> 02:50:43.749
Kill them!

28
02:50:43.958 --> 02:50:45.249
Kill them all!
